<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.713.15118.figures23-35>
    dc:description "Figures 23 - 35. 23 - 26 Euborellia janeirensis (male): habitus (23), penultimate sternite + manubrium (24), and genitalia (25, 26) 27 - 28 Euborellia janeirensis (female): habitus (27), and spermatheca (28) 29 - 32 Euborellia brasiliensis (male): habitus (29), penultimate sternite + manubrium (30), and genitalia (31, 32) 33 Anisolabididae gen. sp. 1 (female): habitus 34 Anisolabididae gen. sp. 2 (nymph): habitus 35 Anisolabididae gen. sp. 3 (nymph) habitus. Scale bars 3 mm for Figs 23 - 25, 27, 29, 30, 33 - 35; 0.5 mm for Figs 26, 28, 31; 100 μm for Fig. 32." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/165934" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

